@obiwan90/edgedb-mcp-server
EdgeDB MCP Server is a tool based on the Model Context Protocol (MCP) that provides query and management capabilities for EdgeDB databases. It can be used as a command-line tool or integrated as a library into other projects. *Database Management Tools* - Connect to databases (supports DSN and instance name) - List available databases - Create new databases - Switch current database - Get current database information *Query Tools* - Execute EdgeQL queries - Execute EdgeQL queries with parameters - Find single records - Find multiple records (with filtering, sorting, pagination) *Schema Management Tools* - List types (optionally including system types) - Get type details - Compare schema structures
